author: Perez Hilton
title: YouTube Cooking Star Auntie Fee On Life Support After Massive Heart Attack!
text:
Hoping for the best!!!
On Tuesday, YouTube star Auntie Fee suffered a massive heart attack and was put on life support. She is said to be "fighting for her life".
TMZ had previously reported that the beloved cook had died.
Auntie Fee is only 59 years old.
Related: Christina Grimmie's Legacy Lives On! 
The viral personality -- also known as Chef Sista Girl -- experienced chest pains and was vomiting prior to her passing. The chef was eventually transferred to Harbor-UCLA Medical Center .
The Barbershop 3 actress -- whose real name is Felicia O'Dell -- became famous in 2014 when she shared her recipes for "good ass chicken" and "sweet treats for the kids."
Our thoughts and prayers are with Felicia's friends and family during this difficult time.
We will continue to keep you posted on her condition!
[ Image via YouTube . ]
